<h1 id="toc0"><span>Person of Interest File #02222/01 — &quot;Aethris&quot;</span></h1>
<p><strong>Legal Name:</strong> ███████ ████</p>
<p><strong>Known Aliases:</strong> Aethris, Aethris_Art, Aestrei</p>
<p><strong>Reason for Interest:</strong> Person of Interest possesses a sizable collection of memetic artwork, despite having no connections to any known anart-related Groups of Interest. Potentially a Type-III ontokinetic entity.</p>
<p><strong>Description:</strong> Aethris (appearing as Aestrei and Aethris_Art on the Reddit and Twitter social media platforms respectively) is an amateur producer of anomalous art with a wide variety of different styles, ranging from digital painting to pixel art.</p>
